        <span data-fontsize="11">th</span>
        <span data-contrast="auto">
          <span> day would be enabled for Customer to choose </span>
          <span>from</span>
          <span> and the next 8 days would also be enabled for a total of 10 enabled days. These dates are all excluding weekends.</span>
        </span>
