    <span>In Edit Case scenario, for any line item, if the earlier entitlement check date is on same day, we will not be doing the Entitlement check for that Line item again and we use earlier data but if any new line items are added then the Entitlement check API will be Called out for the newly added Line Items. </span>
    <span data-ccp-props="{}"> </span>
  </li>
</ul>
<ul>
  <li data-aria-level="2" data-aria-posinset="2" data-font="Courier New" data-leveltext="o" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:1440,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Courier New&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[9675],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;o&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="24" data-uuid="8886fa73-fbb7-4527-94f6-76cee69e0895">
